        <eAnnotations source="http://www.eclipse.org/emf/2002/GenModel">
          <details key="documentation" value="A dependency relationship that specifies a transition from one Asset, Standard, Competence to another future one. It is related to an ActualEnterprisePhase to give it a temporal context."/>
