      <details key="documentation" value="Stakeholders: Solution Providers, Systems Engineers, Business Architects, Human Resources. 
Concerns: the analysis.e.g. evaluation of different alternatives, what-if, trade-offs, V&amp;V on the actual resource configurations. 
Definition: illustrates the expected or achieved actual resource configurations and actual relationships between them."/>
    </eAnnotations>
